# Privacy and security

- Never send data off-machine. All processing is localhost-only.
- The shareable profile is derived-only: no raw prompt text, no code blocks,
  no file paths beyond project names.
- No secrets in committed files.
- The `data/` directory, `*.config.json`, and `profile.md` must never be committed.
